   class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 720px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 18.333333333333336%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"unicode-range-img3.png\"\n        title=\"unicode-range-img3.png\"\n        src=\"/static/42d6fc01e0a23cfaf155cff9c6dbb385/37523/unicode-range-img3.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/42d6fc01e0a23cfaf155cff9c6dbb385/e9ff0/unicode-range-img3.png 180w,\n/static/42d6fc01e0a23cfaf155cff9c6dbb385/f21e7/unicode-range-img3.png 360w,\n/static/42d6fc01e0a23cfaf155cff9c6dbb385/37523/unicode-range-img3.png 720w,\n/static/42d6fc01e0a23cfaf155cff9c6dbb385/302a4/unicode-range-img3.png 1080w,\n/static/42d6fc01e0a23cfaf155cff9c6dbb385/07a9c/unicode-range-img3.png 1440w,\n/static/42d6fc01e0a23cfaf155cff9c6dbb385/f02b9/unicode-range-img3.png 1554w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>알파벳의 경우 나눔바른고딕체가 적용되었다! <br/>\n우측 상단의 font-family 속성을 통해 한글/알파벳 모두 Nanum Font가 적용되었음을 확인할 수 있다.</p>\n<p>언어, 특수문자에 따라 폰트를 달리하고싶다면 이와 같은 방법으로 unicode와 @font-face를 활용하자.</p>\n<div class=\"table-of-contents\">\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#%EB%93%A4%EC%96%B4%EA%B0%80%EB%A9%B0\">들어가며</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#font-face\">@font-face</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#unicode-range\">unicode-range</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#unicode-range-%EC%B0%B8%EA%B3%A0-%EB%A7%81%ED%81%AC\">unicode-range 참고 링크</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#%EC%A0%81%EC%9A%A9%EC%98%88%EC%8B%9C\">적용예시</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#%EA%B2%B0%EA%